The,US,Census,Bureau,surveys,the,US,population,for,demographic,information,and,provides,this,information,to,the,public,as,well,as,using,the,data,for,decision,making,The,US,Census,Bureau,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,data,from,the,US,Census,Bureau,beginning,with,the,Census,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,data,by,geographic,location,retrieving,summary,files,and,retrieving,demographic,information